*Craig Goldy – guitar 
*Tim &quot;Ripper&quot; Owens – vocals 
*Rudy Sarzo – bass 
*Toby Jepson – vocals 
*James LoMenzo – bass 
*Mark Boals – vocals 
Touring members
*Doro Pesch – vocals 
*Vinny Appice – drums 
*Rowan Robertson – guitar 
*Gonzo Sandoval – drums 
*Joe Retta – vocals 
====Last in Line====

Current members
*Vinny Appice – drums 
*Vivian Campbell – guitar 
*Andrew Freeman – lead vocals 
*Phil Soussan – bass 

Former members
*Jimmy Bain – bass 
*Claude Schnell – keyboards 
*Erik Norlander – keyboards 
