* &quot;Microsoft Train Simulator&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Space Simulator&quot;, and &quot;Microsoft Combat Flight Simulator&quot;
* Training simulation
* Virtual Air Traffic Simulation Network
* X-Plane (simulator)

